  "description": "LFO speed pushed past the Nyquist of musical sense — frequency modulation at rates that create foldback artifacts rather than tremolo. Drive at maximum converting the waveform into something closer to a square than its origin. The classic oscillator as a machine for producing unintended harmonics.",
